sourcesContent:
<Box
    sx={{
        display: 'flex',
        flexDirection: 'column',
        alignItems: 'center',
        justifyContent: 'center',
        height: '100vh',
        position: 'relative', // Ensure proper positioning for the pseudo-element
        backgroundColor: '#f5f5f5',
        padding: 2,
        overflow: 'hidden', // Ensures the blur doesn't extend outside the box
        '&::before': {
            content: '""', // Required for pseudo-element
            position: 'absolute',
            top: 0,
            left: 0,
            width: '100%',
            height: '100%',
            backgroundImage: `url("/seaView.jpg")`,
            backgroundSize: 'cover',
            backgroundPosition: 'center',
            backgroundRepeat: 'no-repeat',
            backgroundAttachment: 'fixed',
            filter: 'blur(5px)', // Blur only the background image
            zIndex: -1, // Ensure the image is behind the content
        },
    }}
>
    {/* Your content here */}
</Box>
